{"id":244,"date":"2025-03-16T22:40:39","date_gmt":"2025-03-16T15:40:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=244"},"modified":"2025-06-05T13:46:22","modified_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:46:22","slug":"da-treatment-la-da-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/da-treatment-la-da-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec? H\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1ch ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Treatment ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef quen thu\u1ed9c v\u1edbi t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 m\u00ea skincare. Nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft? Treatment gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t con dao hai l\u01b0\u1ee1i &#8211; n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sai c\u00e1ch, l\u00e0n da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, bong tr\u00f3c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n. C\u00f9ng GSC kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 <\/span><\/i><b><i>da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da chu\u1ea9n khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-treatment-la-da-gi\"><\/span><b>Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00e0n da \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u1eed l\u00fd c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5n, th\u00e2m, n\u00e1m, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a&#8230; b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Retinol, AHA, BHA, Tretinoin ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n nh\u01b0 peel da, laser.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u00f3i c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c,<\/span> da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">? l\u00e0n da \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u00ec s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u00f4, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuc-hoi-da-sau-treatment-quan-trong-khong\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau treatment quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec th\u00ec c\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u xem ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau treatment quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00f4ng. Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da sau treatment kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu l\u00e0n da, m\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y, da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2584\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2584\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2584 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi.webp\" alt=\"Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2584\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">T\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1: C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u, th\u00e2m n\u00e1m xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n do da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">H\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng: L\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o, khi\u1ebfn da ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng m\u1ecfng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Breakout (b\u00f9ng ph\u00e1t m\u1ee5n): Khi da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da b\u1ecb suy y\u1ebfu, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi khu\u1ea9n, c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng breakout.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">V\u00ec v\u1eady, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da t\u00e1i sinh kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh sau m\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ee3t treatment.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cac-loai-treatment-thuong-gap-hien-nay\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i treatment th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i treatment \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2583\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2583\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2583 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-thanh-phan.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i treatment th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p hi\u1ec7n nay\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-thanh-phan.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-thanh-phan-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-thanh-phan-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/da-treatment-la-da-gi-thanh-phan-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2583\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i treatment th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p hi\u1ec7n nay<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Retinol &amp; Tretinoin: D\u1eabn xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Vitamin A, c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o, t\u0103ng sinh collagen, l\u00e0m d\u00e0y l\u1edbp bi\u1ec3u b\u00ec v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n, th\u00e2m, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AHA (Alpha Hydroxy Acid): Tan trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da gi\u00fap t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u da, l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">BHA (Beta Hydroxy Acid): Tan trong d\u1ea7u, th\u00e2m nh\u1eadp s\u00e2u v\u00e0o l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 x\u1eed l\u00fd m\u1ee5n \u1ea9n, m\u1ee5n \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111en.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vitamin C n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao: Ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a m\u1ea1nh, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh collagen.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Peel da h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao \u0111\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft, k\u00edch th\u00edch t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u1edbp da m\u1edbi m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p gi\u00fap l\u00e0n da nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00e1i sinh v\u00e0 kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da sau treatment th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c, m\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ecf, n\u00f3ng r\u00e1t, ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2m ch\u00edch. Ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 da t\u1ef1 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7n ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u1ebfu v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"phuc-hoi-da-treatment-bi-quyet-lanh-tinh-hieu-qua-ngay-tai-nha\"><\/span><b>Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da treatment: B\u00ed quy\u1ebft l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ngay t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da treatment l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng y\u1ebfu, nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m h\u01a1n c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i da kh\u00e1c. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1eddi gian v\u00e0ng\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, gi\u00fap da ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. V\u1eady, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da sau treatment nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1? C\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay <\/span><b>c\u00e1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng treatment cho da <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dung-quen-buoc-bao-ve\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Tia UV l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da sau treatment \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, s\u1ea1m \u0111en. Tia UV kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, g\u00e2y n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang m\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn da th\u00eam m\u1ecfng y\u1ebfu, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF &gt;30.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thoa \u0111\u1ee7 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng (kho\u1ea3ng 1-1,5 \u0111\u1ed1t ng\u00f3n tay cho m\u1eb7t).<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0 \u0111i bi\u1ec3n, b\u01a1i th\u00ec n\u00ean thoa l\u1ea1i sau 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 4 gi\u1edd sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p m\u0169 r\u1ed9ng v\u00e0nh, k\u00ednh r\u00e2m v\u00e0 qu\u1ea7n \u00e1o d\u00e0i tay \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-sach-nhe-nhang\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n <em>L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng<\/em>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1eeba ph\u1ea3i, kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 l\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Massage m\u1eb7t theo chi\u1ec1u n\u00e2ng c\u01a1<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">R\u1eeda s\u1ea1ch l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-toner\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng toner<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u01b0\u1edbc toner gi\u00fap da c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH, gi\u00fap da h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecdn toner ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u01afu ti\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i toner d\u1ea1ng x\u1ecbt, c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gi\u00fap c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da t\u1ee9c th\u00ec<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cap-am-cho-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">C\u1ea5p \u1ea9m cho da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec &#8211; D\u00f9 da b\u1ea1n l\u00e0 da d\u1ea7u, da kh\u00f4 hay h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p, d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i nh\u01b0 B5, ceramide, HA.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">L\u1ea5y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ea3n ph\u00e2m v\u1eeba \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5m s\u00e2u.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da \u0111\u1ee7 \u1ea9m s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng bong tr\u00f3c, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u m\u1ea5t ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"serum-chuyen-phuc-hoi-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Serum chuy\u00ean ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0n da nhanh ch\u00f3ng ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u. T\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a EGF, FGF, Sodium DNA, Bifida Ferment Lysate.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>&gt;&gt; xem th\u00eam: serum ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da treatment \u201cGSC Advanced Repair Serum\u2019 &#8211; Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da treatment hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3<\/b><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tai-sao-cang-treatment-da-cang-xau\"><\/span><b>T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e0ng treatment da c\u00e0ng x\u1ea5u?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Da treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec &#8211; Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u00ean tr\u00ec treatment nh\u01b0ng m\u00e3i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y da \u0111\u1eb9p l\u00ean. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_2585\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-2585\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-2585 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/dau-hieu-da-treatment-la-da-gi.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e0ng treatment da c\u00e0ng x\u1ea5u?\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/dau-hieu-da-treatment-la-da-gi.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/dau-hieu-da-treatment-la-da-gi-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/dau-hieu-da-treatment-la-da-gi-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/03\/dau-hieu-da-treatment-la-da-gi-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-2585\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>T\u1ea1i sao c\u00e0ng treatment da c\u00e0ng x\u1ea5u?<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ch\u1ecdn sai ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t ho\u1eb7c n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 Retinol qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn da breakout. Ngo\u00e0i ra, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng BHA n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 cao l\u00e0m da bong tr\u00f3c qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p, quan s\u00e1t ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng da r\u1ed3i t\u0103ng d\u1ea7n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Sai t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng: Vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng retinol m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u hay peel da qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Retinol n\u00ean d\u00f9ng 2-3 l\u1ea7n\/tu\u1ea7n khi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, peel da ch\u1ec9 n\u00ean l\u00e0m 1 l\u1ea7n\/th\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Thi\u1ebfu b\u01b0\u1edbc ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i: Ch\u1ec9 d\u00f9ng ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t treatment m\u00e0 qu\u00ean d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng. Da sau treatment r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u1ee9a B5, Hyaluronic Acid.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7: C\u1ea7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 SPF 30+ tr\u1edf l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1, l\u00e3o h\u00f3a.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Kh\u00f4ng l\u1eafng nghe l\u00e0n da: Da \u0111\u1ecf r\u00e1t, bong tr\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00f9ng treatment. Khi da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng, gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t, t\u0103ng d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m, tr\u00e1nh th\u00eam s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft \u201cda treatment l\u00e0 da g\u00ec\u201d hay \u201ctreatment da l\u00e0 g\u00ec\u201d r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00fang kh\u00f4ng? C\u00f9ng GSC t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c hay ho c\u00f9ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i nh\u00e9. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean theo d\u00f5i GSC \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ecf t\u00fai th\u00eam cho m\u00ecnh th\u1eadt nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed9i dung v\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m h\u1eefu \u00edch.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>GSC b\u1eadt m\u00ed c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t &#8220;\u0111\u1ec9nh&#8221; nh\u1ea5t n\u0103m 2025 v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":4,"featured_media":2582,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[8],"class_list":["post-244","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong","tag-new"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/244","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/4"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=244"}],"version-history":[{"count":9,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/244\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3873,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/244\/revisions\/3873"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2582"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=244"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=244"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=244"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}